      "n": 14,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Ja tam daudſ Behrnu\nbuhs/ tad Sohbins pahr teem\nnahks/ un winna Pehz nahka-\nmee ne pee-ehtdiſees ar Matsi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 15,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winna Atliffafchee pa-\nschá Nahwē taps aprakti/ un\nwinna Atraitnes ne raundahs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 16,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Kad winſch Nauda fa-\nkrahs ka Pihſchlus/ un Drehbes\nfadohmahs ka Mahlus.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 17,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tad winſch to gann ta-\ndohmahs/ bet tas Taisnajs tahe\napwilks/ un tas Nenoseedſigajs\nto Naudu dallihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 18,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Winſch ustaifa fawu\nNaimmu ka weena * Kohda/ un\nka Gans weenu Buhdu padarra.\n* Ka weena Kohda, kis eekſch dahrgahm\nDrehbehm eekohſchahs, bet tohp ahtri atkat is-\nmesta.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 19,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Baggatajs/ kad tas\napgullahs/ tad winſch ne taps *\npeelikts / winſch atdarrihs fa-\nwas Azzie/ un ne buhs wairs.\n* Tas irr, wiſch ne taps aprakts.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 20,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Bailiba tam usbruks ka\nUhdens/ Nakti winnu weens\nWeetuls aisweddihs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 21,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Tas Auſtrina Wehjſch\nwinnu aisweddihs ka tas aiseet/\nun isputtinahs winnu no fawas\nWeetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 22,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Wiſch to pahr winnu\nmettihs/ unne taupihs/ no win-\nna Rohkas wiſs behdsin isbehgs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 23,
      "column": "left",
      "text": "Pahr winnu fatittihs\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Plauſtes/ un ſwitpehs p\nwinnu no winna Weetas.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta XXVIII. Nodalla.\nFiabs mahja/ ka Deewa Gndriba neiſw\njama effu : 1. Kur tomehr wiſas apſ\ntas Leetas zaar Zilweſo Prahtu warr iſ\nnitas tapt : 2/4/12/14. Ta wiſule\nGndriba weena Zilweſa irr/ Deewu bih\nun no Launa atſahtees : 28.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 1,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Eefcham / Sudrab\nSirr fawi Zetti / un E\nStam irr Weeta/ fur\nkanſehts tohp.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 2,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Dselse tohp no Semm\nxemta / un no Akminxeem te\nWarſch leets.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 3,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "To Gallu / ko (Deew\ntai Tuimſibai lizzis / un wi\ndas Leetas tas (Zilweſs) pa-\nmannia/ ir tohs paſchá Tuimf\napſlechptus Akminius.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 4,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winſch isplehtch to Ge\nju/ fur ne weens dſthwojs/ ko\nkahda Kahja ne finn/ ta no-\nun tohp kuſtinata no ta Zilwe\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 5,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ta Semme/ no ka Ma\nnahk/ tahs Appakſcha tohp\nwehrtita/ itt ka (no) Uggun\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 6,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Winnas Akmini irr\nwiu Weeta/ un eekſch tahs\nSelts Pihſchlſchi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 7,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "Ne kahds Putnis irr\nZettu atſinnis / un ne kat\nWannaga Azf irr to redsejſi.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 8,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "To breeſmigu Swe\nBehrni us to ue irr minnuſc\nun ne kahds wezz Lauwa us\nirr ſtaigajs.\n"
    },
    {
      "n": 9,
      "column": "right",
      "text": "( Tas Zilweſs ) per\n"
    }
  ],
